class="block-intro-text"><p>Physical therapy websites help practices promote their services and attract new patients. High-quality visuals conveying a professional, welcoming practice atmosphere inspire confidence, and compelling service descriptions and resources help to sell patients on the benefits of your services, with reviews and qualifications providing reassurance.</p><p>Team profiles and an "About" section add a human touch, while clear CTAs and an online booking system get visitors to engage and schedule appointments. To get started on your site, use our <a
href="/">AI-powered physical therapy website builder</a>, which will create a fully-fledged website complete with content in under a minute.</p></div><div
