<span>New York, New York, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>In Touch NYC Physical Therapy is a clinic based in Manhattan that provides one-on-one physical therapy sessions that include corrective exercises, functional training activities, and Pilates. Their website stood out to me for its beautifully balanced and consistent branding across its pages, instantly lending it a smart, professional appeal that inspires confidence.</p><p>It also displays information in a visually engaging manner, with plenty of custom imagery, and features ample CTAs, along with a live chat feature, making it very easy for site visitors to contact the clinic.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
